To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private Piercing _piercing;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_piercing = Piercing(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_piercing.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "Piercing Period", _piercing.Period);
    Plot("My Indicators", "Piercing Current", _piercing.Current);
